snippet.title: The second promotional trailer for the psychic action shooter FALLEN.
snippet.description:
The psychic action shooter FALLEN is launching on August 30, 2024.
Check out Steam store page.

To celebrate the release of FALLEN, we're having a one-week sale! You can purchase the game at 10% off, so don't miss this opportunity!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2725000/FALLEN/
